name: Checking a date via date picker using input field
fullName: features/ui/widget_interactions_with_input_fields.feature#Checking a date via date picker using input field

steps.name: I navigate to Demoqa Home page
Given I navigate to Date Picker page
When I type "10/10/2022" in the Select Date field
Then the date picked is "Monday, October 10th, 2022"
